Translator Log Discord Bot - Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 14.01.2024

1. Overview

Translator Log ("the Bot") is committed to protecting the privacy of its users. This Privacy Policy outlines how the Bot collects, uses, discloses, and safeguards user information.

2. Information Collected

Server Data: The Bot may collect data from Discord servers it is added to, including but not limited to messages, user IDs, and server configurations.

User Preferences: The Bot may store user preferences and settings for a better user experience.

3. Use of Information

Service Improvement: Collected information is used to enhance and improve the functionality of the Bot.

Communication: The Bot may use collected data to communicate important information, updates, or announcements to users.

4. Data Security

The Bot takes reasonable measures to protect user data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is entirely secure.

5. Data Sharing

The Bot does not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer user information to external parties. However, certain data may be shared with third-party services for the sole purpose of providing and maintaining the Bot's services.

6. Cookies

The Bot may use cookies to enhance the user experience. Users can adjust their browser settings to refuse cookies but may experience limitations in Bot functionality.

7. Changes to Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated to reflect changes in data processing practices. Users will be notified of significant changes via the Bot or other communication channels.

8. Third-Party Services

The Bot may utilize third-party services. Users are encouraged to review the privacy policies of these services for a complete understanding of their data practices.

9. User Rights

Users have the right to request access, correction, or deletion of their personal information. For inquiries regarding user rights or any privacy concerns, please contact Discord: dxrkt.

10. Contact Information

For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact Translator Log at Discord: dxrkt.

By using the Bot, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
